$SIZES LVR=35 $PROBLEM //like/1045//but/dropping off diagonals// $INPUT C STDY ID USUBJID=DROP IGDA=DROP IGTI=DROP OCC RTFD=TIME RTLD NTIM AMT DV LNDV LLOQ DVCODE=DROP CMT EVID MDV SERIAL DOSE1 TRTARM COH FREQ DAY AGE AGEC BWT WT BSA SEX ETHN RACE FORM FED GVHD BCRCL CRCL ALT AST ALB TBIL TYPE AZOLE CYPI OATPI CYCLP FIASM PPI STEROID TACRO SIRO REP $DATA CMX001-all_01Mar16_cov.csv IGNORE=(C.EQ.C) IGNORE=(C.GT.0) $SUBROUTINE ADVAN5 TRANS1 $MODEL COMP=ABS ;(DEFDOSE) COMP=CENTRAL ;(DEFOBS) COMP=PERI COMP=CDV COMP=PERI2 $PK
; CONTCOV NWT, NAG, NCR ; CATCOV SUS, TAB, FED, CYC, CYP, GH1, GH2, GH3, GH4 NWT = WT/70 NAG = AGE/40 CRL = CRCL IF(CRL.GT.150) CRL = 150 NCR= CRL/85 SUS = 0 TAB = 0 FDF = 0 IF(FORM.EQ.1) SUS = 1 IF(FORM.EQ.2) TAB = 1 IF(FED.EQ.1) FDF = 1 CYC = CYCLP CYP = CYPI GHX = 0 IF(GVHD.EQ.1) GHX = 1 IF(GVHD.EQ.2) GHX = 1 IF(GVHD.EQ.3) GHX = 1 IF(GVHD.EQ.4) GHX = 1
TCL = THETA(1) TV2 = THETA(2) TQA = THETA(3) TV3 = THETA(4) TLAG = THETA(5) TKA = THETA(6) TCLM = THETA(7) TVM1 = THETA(8) TQM = THETA(9) TVM2 = THETA(10)
CLA = TCL * EXP(ETA(1)) * NWT ** THETA(11) * NAG ** THETA(19) * NCR ** THETA(21) * THETA(23) ** CYC * THETA(25) ** CYP VA1 = TV2 * EXP(ETA(2)) * NWT ** THETA(12) QA = TQA * EXP(ETA(3)) * NWT ** THETA(13) VA2 = TV3 * EXP(ETA(4)) * NWT ** THETA(14) ALAG1= TLAG * EXP(ETA(5)) * THETA(27) ** FDF * THETA(30) ** SUS * THETA(33) ** TAB K12 = TKA * EXP(ETA(6)) * THETA(28) ** FDF * THETA(31) ** SUS * THETA(34) ** TAB CLM = TCLM * EXP(ETA(7)) * NWT ** THETA(15) * NAG ** THETA(20) * NCR ** THETA(22) * THETA(24) ** CYC * THETA(26) ** CYP VM1 = TVM1 * EXP(ETA(8)) * NWT ** THETA(16) QM = TQM * EXP(ETA(9)) * NWT ** THETA(17) VM2 = TVM2 * EXP(ETA(10))* NWT ** THETA(18) F1 = EXP(ETA(11)) * THETA(29) ** FDF * THETA(32) ** SUS * THETA(35) ** TAB * THETA(36) ** GHX
K23 = QA / VA1 K32 = QA / VA2 K24 = CLA / VA1 K40 = CLM / VM1 K45 = QM / VM1 K54 = QM / VM2
RT= DSQRT((K23+K32+K24)**2 - (4*K32*K24)) ALPH= ((K23+K32+K24) + RT)/2 BETA= ((K23+K32+K24) - RT)/2 TALPH= 0.693/ALPH T1 = 0.693/BETA RT1= DSQRT((K45+K54+K40)**2 - (4*K54*K40)) BETA2= ((K45+K54+K40) - RT1)/2 T2 = 0.693/BETA2
S2 = VA1 S4 = VM1/0.497 ;CONVERTED TO CMX001 EQUIVALENT
$ERROR IND2 = 0 IND4 = 0 IF (CMT.EQ.2) IND2 = 1 IF (CMT.EQ.4) IND4 = 1
IPRED = F Y2 = F + F * ERR(1) + ERR(2) Y4 = F + F * ERR(3) + ERR(4) Y = Y2 * IND2 + Y4 * IND4
